			</a>
			<br/>
			SET-IT provides a single software tool that integrates
			drawing and database tools with the Architecture Reference for Cooperative & Intelligent Transportation (ARC-IT) so that
			users can develop project architectures for pilots, test beds, and early deployments.
		</p>
		<p>
